<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA47">
<l>niṉaittiṟaiñci māṉiṭava roṉṟirappa reṉṟē</l>
<l>niṉaittiṭavum vēṇṭānī nērē niṉaittiṟaiñca</l>
<l>vevvaḷava revviṭattōr mālē yatutāṉu</l>
<l>mevvaḷavu muṇṭō vemakku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if you have come to think human beings, thinking [of you</l>
<l>and] bowing, will beg for something, there is no need. To think straight</l>
<l>[of you and] bow, how many, in which place are they, Māl? And that itself,</l>
<l>how much is it to us?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
